today was fun and shitty went to my sisters graduation. hung out with jake most the time. that was cool i suppose. he is very touchy. then i went on the feild like everyone does to take pictures and such. i was secretly wanting to see him the whole time. looking around and hoping for maybe one second of eye contact. and then i see him. and then i see my mother hugging him. and kiss him on the cheek. i was very upset. I wanted to be the one hugging him. I wanted to be the one kissing him on the cheek. I wanted to be the one congratulating him on graduating highschool. but no. thats pretty sad im jealous of my mother. but yes i saw him. no eye contact. no nothing. i doubt he even saw me. he just looks right through me. its like im invisable or something. i felt really embarrased because i wanted to cry So bad because i know that i will probably never see him again. and i thought i could hold it in but this time i couldnt. im just glad it wasnt untill we were in the parking lot. i couldnt have let him see me cry again. he would think im weak and thats something i cant be. thats why i pretend to hate him and pretend to think he is really ugly and such all my real friends know that im pretending but they go along with it. i dont know. i just. i wonder if he ever thinks of me. i wonder if he sometimes lays in bed at night and just thinks about me. because thats what i find myself doing everynight before i go to bed. i want to know so badly what was going on inside of his mind april.21 when he drove away from my house for the last time after just breaking my heart. did he feel sad? happy? free? i hope he doesnt forget me. i feel like he somewhat has. i feel like when he sees me he just looks past me like im just some girl who he had a class with or something like that. i dont know. it is shitty. i wish we still talked but that is never going to happen. it is impossible because everytime we speak i have the urge to tell him how badly i need him back. i just want to spill my heart out to him and tell him how everything was perfect when he was here. even when we were fighting. i want to tell him how he could ALWAYS make me feel better. i want to tell him how shitty things have been without him. i want to tell him how SORRY i am for whatever i did that made him fall out of love with me. but i cant. he wouldnt understand. and thats just something ill have to learn to accept
